<p class="bac">
Associates will participate in a formal Education and Orientation program to learn more about Bank&nbsp;of&nbsp;America business, culture and values, as well as to network with Executives and other college hires.  Additionally, interns will participate in various networking and learning opportunities throughout the duration of the program. 
</p>

